# API Matcher

A FastAPI-based service that matches resumes with job descriptions using automated text analysis and scoring.

## Features

* Upload and analyze resumes
* Compare resumes against job descriptions
* Generate match scores
* Highlight relevant skills and keywords
* RESTful API endpoints
* Fast and lightweight implementation

## Tech Stack

* Python
* FastAPI
* SQLAlchemy
* Pydantic
* PostgreSQL / SQLite

## Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/3bth10/api-matcher.git
cd api-matcher

python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate   # Linux/Mac
venv\Scripts\activate      # Windows

pip install -r requirements.txt
```

## Run the API

```bash
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

The API will be available at:

```text
http://localhost:8000
```

## API Documentation

Swagger UI:

```text
http://localhost:8000/docs
```

ReDoc:

```text
http://localhost:8000/redoc
```

## Example Workflow

1. Upload a resume.
2. Submit a job description.
3. Receive a compatibility score.
4. Review matched skills and recommendations.

